    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained. The exterior paint still holds a strong luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scratch near the driver's door handle. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only light wear on the seat bolsters and floor mats consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car is sound, shifting smoothly and handling well, making it an excellent choice for someone seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the premium price of a mint-condition model.",
