    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an impeccably maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This specimen has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, this automobile offers a refined driving experience consistent with its prestigious provenance. It represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle that balances luxury with enduring value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
